藥劑師配藥價格（或稱處方費用（prescription cost））的定義是患者根據醫師開立的處方箋，獲得藥物或治療而必須支付的費用。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dictionary.cambridge.org/us/dictionary/english/prescription|title=PRESCRIPTION {{!}} definition in the Cambridge English Dictionary|website=dictionary.cambridge.org|access-date=2019-10-23|archive-date=2019-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191023035647/https://dictionary.cambridge.org/us/dictionary/english/prescription|dead-url=no}}</ref>成本通常受到藥廠、批發分銷商、和藥房之間財務關係的影響。<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=https://www.kff.org/other/report/follow-the-pill-understanding-the-u-s/|title=Follow The Pill: Understanding the U.S. Commercial Pharmaceutical Supply Chain|date=2005-02-28|website=The Henry J. Kaiser Family Foundation|access-date=2019-10-23}}</ref>除了財務關係，每個國家都會利用不同的系統來控制[[處方藥|處方藥]]的成本。在美國，[[藥品福利管理|藥品福利管理者]]，第三方組織（例如私人保險或政府運作的醫療保險）會設立成本控制計劃，例如建立[[處方集|處方表]]，以控制成本。<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424053111903554904576460322664055328|title=What is a 'Pharmacy Benefit Manager?'|last=Gryta|first=Thomas|date=2011-07-21|work=Wall Street Journal|access-date=2019-10-23|issn=0099-9660|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015222254/https://www.wsj.com/articles/SB10001424053111903554904576460322664055328|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[英國|英國]]，政府會與[[製藥產業|製藥產業]]談判，共同制定藥品費用增長的整體上限，另外，{{link-en|國家卓越醫療衛生研究所|National Institute of Health and Care Excellence}}（NICE）還會針對各個處方藥定價的成本效益做評估。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pharmaceutical-technology.com/features/cost-control-drug-pricing-policies-around-world/|title=Cost control: drug pricing policies around the world|access-date=2019-10-23|archive-date=2021-01-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120002131/https://www.pharmaceutical-technology.com/features/cost-control-drug-pricing-policies-around-world/|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[國民保健署|國民保健署]]（NHS）也會直接與各個藥廠就某些特殊藥品進行價格談判，以及在有多種[[通用名藥物|通用名藥物]]或是專利藥物可用於治療相同病症的情況時，採用競價的採購方式。<ref>{{Cite web|title=NHS England partners with Gilead, Merck, AbbVie in billion-pound hepatitis C eradication push|url=https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/nhs-england-picks-gilead-for-massive-hep-c-contract|access-date=2021-04-18|website=FiercePharma|language=en|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420213111/https://www.fiercepharma.com/pharma/nhs-england-picks-gilead-for-massive-hep-c-contract|dead-url=no}}</ref>處方費用是病人的常規醫療費用，對弱勢群體來說就意味著經濟壓力。<ref name="NYT-20151219">{{cite news |author=The Editorial Board |title=No Justification for High Drug Prices |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/opinion/sunday/no-justification-for-high-drug-prices.html |date=2015-12-19 |work=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]] |access-date=2015-12-20 |archive-date=2020-12-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201220202627/https://www.nytimes.com/2015/12/20/opinion/sunday/no-justification-for-high-drug-prices.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>美國的患者有了[[醫療保險|醫療保險]]，對於處方費用需要支付[[共付額|共付額]]（患者每次在領藥或者就診必須支付的金額）、[[自負額_(醫療保險)|自負額]]（患者在保險公司開始分擔費用之前，必須自行支付的金額）、和[[共同保險|共同保險]]費用（患者在支付自負額後，必須與保險公司共同負擔的金額）。<ref name=":8">{{Cite web|url=https://www.investopedia.com/terms/h/healthinsurance.asp|title=What Is Health Insurance?|last=Kagan|first=Julia|website=Investopedia|language=en|access-date=2019-10-31|archive-date=2021-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210428030837/https://www.investopedia.com/terms/h/healthinsurance.asp|dead-url=no}}</ref>達到患者保險中的[[自付費用|自付費用]]上限後，保險公司就需對於其餘的費用作100％的支付。<ref name=":8" />患者支付的金額數目，取決於他們所擁有醫療保險計劃的條件。<ref name=":8" />

截至2017年，處方費用對GDP的比率，從高收入國家的15％以上，到中低收入國家和低收入國家的25％不等。<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Wirtz VJ, Hogerzeil HV, Gray AL, Bigdeli M, de Joncheere CP, Ewen MA, Gyansa-Lutterodt M, Jing S, Luiza VL, Mbindyo RM, Möller H, Moucheraud C, Pécoul B, Rägo L, Rashidian A, Ross-Degnan D, Stephens PN, Teerawattananon Y, 't Hoen EF, Wagner AK, Yadav P, Reich MR | display-authors = 6 | title = Essential medicines for universal health coverage | journal = Lancet | volume = 389 | issue = 10067 | pages = 403–476 | date = January 2017 | pmid = 27832874 | doi = 10.1016/S0140-6736(16)31599-9 | pmc = 7159295 }}</ref>{{rp|418}}

